			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>When swarming your pet will tend to change to targets frequently... it usually attacks whatever has done the most damage to it.  For example, when swarming a mixed bag of yard trash mobs in PoN, I frequently see my pet change from a treant to a raven.  It has never caused me any aggro issues in the past, I'm always able to keep aggro on the pet.  I think there's something else at work here, maybe he is too close to his pet.  I've pulled a few loose mobs off my pet by getting too close when I have, say, 6+ in a swarm.</span></td>
